      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/nick-denton-on-elon-musk-byd-cars-and-the-us-vs-europe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[ Gawker创始人在匈牙利和中国的赌注。]]></description>
