      <title>Nikkei 225进入更正，因为美国关税担心撞到出口商</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/japanese-shares-plunge-as-us-tariff-worries-hit-exporter-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本的蓝筹股Nikkei 225股票的平均水平低落，以进行技术更正，因为出口商和与芯片有关的股票在对全球贸易战的担忧时滑落。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/japanese-shares-plunge-as-us-tariff-worries-hit-exporter-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 01:04:24 GMT</pubDate>
